outputs.output_descr:
Output 1: Generation of sustainable financial and other incentives for conservation of wild relatives at the county level in eight provinces;
Output 2: The policy, legal and regulatory system supports conservation of wild relatives;
Output 3: Stakeholders at the central and local level have adequate capacity to conserve wild relatives;
Output4: Accurate and timely information concerning the status of wild relatives is available and utilized;
Output5: Lessons and experiences from target provinces create conditions for replication and expansion of conservation programmes.
